creator: StoryHunt
descriptionHtml:
Explore your surroundings like never before! Locate the unique stories that hide in plain sight. Whenever you get close to a story, you can unlock it and learn what happened right where you stand.

Pick one of our many tours to gain new knowledge about your surroundings. Unlike a traditional tour guide you go when you want and at your own pace. Whether you are into historical sagas, ghost stories or something else we have a tour for you!

Quality is a keyword when we create tours for StoryHunt. Check out our StoryHunt Originals which are created by journalists, actors and audio specialists. Whether you are a curious local or an adventurous traveller, we promise it will be worth your time.

StoryHunt is well suited for a solo walk if you wish to reflect and learn something new about your surroundings. If you want to make it a social experience you can create a group and explore together.

You can find StoryHunt tours in the following cities:
Copenhagen
Aarhus
Aalborg
Odense
Linkoping
Jonkoping
Hillerød
… with many more to come!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We are happy to announce that the StoryHunt app has finally landed for the Android platform.
